  m_text: 'Thank you for trying out "Follow the Light".

    I cannot wait for your
    feedback! This is a sample scene, containing multiple mechanics to be tested.


    Follow
    the light you cast on objects to find your way through the darkness.


    Movement:
    WASD / ZQSD

    Camera: L&R Arrow keys.

    Camera Preset Angles: C

    Jump:
    Space button


    Toggle Hard Mode: H


    In case of bug, reset your position
    using R button. '
